message.text:
𝐒𝐀𝐑𝐀𝐇 𝐄𝐋𝐀𝐆𝐎 𝐓𝐎 𝐁𝐄 𝐏𝐑𝐎𝐂𝐋𝐀𝐈𝐌𝐄𝐃 𝐀𝐒 𝟔𝟒𝐓𝐇 𝐏𝐀𝐑𝐓𝐘-𝐋𝐈𝐒𝐓 𝐑𝐄𝐏𝐑𝐄𝐒𝐄𝐍𝐓𝐀𝐓𝐈𝐕𝐄 🔔

Commission on Elections Chairman George Erwin Garcia announced on Sunday, September 14, that Gabriela party-list’s first nominee, Sarah Elago, will be proclaimed as the 64th winning party-list representative in the 2025 elections.

This proclamation ensures the constitutional requirement that party-list representatives make up 20 percent of the House of Representatives is fulfilled.

Laging tandaan, ang TAM na boto, dapat TAMang Boto!
#TAMangBoto

message.text:
𝐒𝐀𝐑𝐀𝐇 𝐄𝐋𝐀𝐆𝐎 𝐓𝐎 𝐁𝐄 𝐏𝐑𝐎𝐂𝐋𝐀𝐈𝐌𝐄𝐃 𝐀𝐒 𝟔𝟒𝐓𝐇 𝐏𝐀𝐑𝐓𝐘-𝐋𝐈𝐒𝐓 𝐑𝐄𝐏𝐑𝐄𝐒𝐄𝐍𝐓𝐀𝐓𝐈𝐕𝐄 🔔

Commission on Elections Chairman George Erwin Garcia announced on Sunday, September 14, that Gabriela party-list’s first nominee, Sarah Elago, will be proclaimed as the 64th winning party-list representative in the 2025 elections.

This proclamation ensures the constitutional requirement that party-list representatives make up 20 percent of the House of Representatives is fulfilled.

Laging tandaan, ang TAM na boto, dapat TAMang Boto!
#TAMangBoto

message.text:
𝐒𝐀𝐑𝐀𝐇 𝐄𝐋𝐀𝐆𝐎 𝐓𝐎 𝐁𝐄 𝐏𝐑𝐎𝐂𝐋𝐀𝐈𝐌𝐄𝐃 𝐀𝐒 𝟔𝟒𝐓𝐇 𝐏𝐀𝐑𝐓𝐘-𝐋𝐈𝐒𝐓 𝐑𝐄𝐏𝐑𝐄𝐒𝐄𝐍𝐓𝐀𝐓𝐈𝐕𝐄 🔔

Commission on Elections Chairman George Erwin Garcia announced on Sunday, September 14, that Gabriela party-list’s first nominee, Sarah Elago, will be proclaimed as the 64th winning party-list representative in the 2025 elections.

This proclamation ensures the constitutional requirement that party-list representatives make up 20 percent of the House of Representatives is fulfilled.

Laging tandaan, ang TAM na boto, dapat TAMang Boto!
#TAMangBoto
